sports/1324108-cape-breton-highlanders-to-hit-the-hardwood\n | accessdate = 2015-12-17\n | newspaper = The Chronicle Herald\n | date = 2015-11-24\n | location = Halifax\n | ref = harv\n}}\n* {{cite news\n | last = McNeil\n | first = Greg\n | title = Cape Breton's NBL franchise will be known as the Highlanders\n | url = http://www.capebretonpost.com/Sports/2015-11-24/article-4354515/Cape-Bretons-NBL-franchise-will-be-known-as-the-Highlanders/1\n | access-date = 2015-12-17\n | newspaper = Cape Breton Post\n | date = 2015-11-24\n | location = Sydney, Nova Scotia\n | ref = harv\n | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222135658/http://www.capebretonpost.com/Sports/2015-11-24/article-4354515/Cape-Bretons-NBL-franchise-will-be-known-as-the-Highlanders/1\n | archive-date = 22 December 2015\n | url-status = dead\n }}\n* {{cite news\n | last = Jala\n | first = David\n | title = CBRM forges relationship with progressive Chinese city\n | url = http://www.capebretonpost.com/News/Local/2015-12-16/article-4378237/CBRM-forges-relationship-with-progressive-Chinese-city/1\n | access-date = 2015-12-17\n | newspaper = Cape Breton Post\n | date = 2015-12-16\n | location = Sydney, Nova Scotia\n | ref = harv\n | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222090628/http://www.capebretonpost.com/News/Local/2015-12-16/article-4378237/CBRM-forges-relationship-with-progressive-Chinese-city/1\n | archive-date = 22 December 2015\n | url-status = dead\n }}\n{{Refend}}\n\n; Other online sources\n{{Refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite web\n | title = Radio History: CJCB-AM, Sydney, Maritime Broadcasting Ltd.\n | url = http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/index3.html?url=http%3A//www.broadcasting-history.ca/listings_and_histories/radio/histories.php%3Fid%3D679%26historyID%3D266\n | publisher = Canadian Communications Foundation\n | year = 2013\n | access-date = 2013-01-10\n | location = Toronto\n | ref = {{harvid|Canadian Communications Foundation|2013}}\n | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/w